#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn15.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Sāvakasutta "
msgstr "7. Disciples "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.183, sc1
msgctxt "sn15.7:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.7:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yena bhagavā … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "Then several mendicants went up to the Buddha … and asked him, "

msgctxt "sn15.7:1.3"
msgid "“kīvabahukā nu kho, bhante, kappā abbhatītā atikkantā”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, how many eons have passed?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.7:1.4"
msgid "“Bahukā kho, bhikkhave, kappā abbhatītā atikkantā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, many eons have passed. "

msgctxt "sn15.7:1.5"
msgid "Te na sukarā saṅkhātuṃ: "
msgstr "It’s not easy to calculate "

msgctxt "sn15.7:1.6"
msgid "‘ettakā kappā iti vā, ettakāni kappasatāni iti vā, ettakāni kappasahassāni iti vā, ettakāni kappasatasahassāni iti vā’”ti. "
msgstr "how many eons have passed, how many hundreds or thousands or hundreds of thousands of eons.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn15.7:2.1"
msgid "“Sakkā pana, bhante, upamaṃ kātun”ti? "
msgstr "“But sir, is it possible to give a simile?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.7:2.2"
msgid "“Sakkā, bhikkhave”ti bhagavā avoca. "
msgstr "“It’s possible,” said the Buddha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.7:2.3"
msgid "“Idhassu, bhikkhave, cattāro sāvakā vassasatāyukā vassasatajīvino. "
msgstr "“Suppose there were four disciples with a lifespan of a hundred years. "

msgctxt "sn15.7:2.4"
msgid "Te divase divase kappasatasahassaṃ kappasatasahassaṃ anussareyyuṃ. "
msgstr "And each day they would each recollect a hundred thousand eons. "

msgctxt "sn15.7:2.5"
msgid "Ananussaritāva, bhikkhave, tehi kappā assu, atha kho te cattāro sāvakā vassasatāyukā vassasatajīvino vassasatassa accayena kālaṃ kareyyuṃ. "
msgstr "Those four disciples would pass away after a hundred years and there would still be eons that they haven’t recollected. "

msgctxt "sn15.7:2.6"
msgid "Evaṃ bahukā kho, bhikkhave, kappā abbhatītā atikkantā. "
msgstr "That’s how many eons have passed. "

msgctxt "sn15.7:2.7"
msgid "Te na sukarā saṅkhātuṃ: "
msgstr "It’s not easy to calculate "

msgctxt "sn15.7:2.8"
msgid "‘ettakā kappā iti vā, ettakāni kappasatāni iti vā, ettakāni kappasahassāni iti vā, ettakāni kappasatasahassāni iti vā’ti. "
msgstr "how many eons have passed, how many hundreds or thousands or hundreds of thousands of eons. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.7:2.9"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn15.7:2.10"
msgid "Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro … pe … "
msgstr "Transmigration has no known beginning. … "

msgctxt "sn15.7:2.11"
msgid "alaṃ vimuccitun”ti. "
msgstr "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.7:2.12"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

